22
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:32,410
 ♫ Reborn in the wheel of fate ♫ 

23
00:01:36,020 --> 00:01:38,940
 

24
00:02:07,760 --> 00:02:09,970
The cold poison is acting up more frequently now.

25
00:02:09,970 --> 00:02:12,820
I must get my hands on the Sunwarm Jade today.

26
00:02:20,760 --> 00:02:21,790
Who's there?

27
00:02:21,790 --> 00:02:23,940
Li.

28
00:02:23,940 --> 00:02:27,300
- Who are you? 
 -

29
00:02:52,660 --> 00:02:54,520
Open the door.

30
00:03:15,540 --> 00:03:17,750
Just you alone?

31
00:03:17,750 --> 00:03:19,820
You don't look well.

32
00:03:19,820 --> 00:03:21,770
Are you very sick?

33
00:03:21,770 --> 00:03:23,850
How did you find me?

34
00:03:23,850 --> 00:03:27,940
Anyone can see that tall guard of yours.

35
00:03:27,940 --> 00:03:29,700
What do you want?

36
00:03:30,970 --> 00:03:32,520
Here.

37
00:03:33,610 --> 00:03:34,850
Sunwarm Jade.

38
00:03:34,850 --> 00:03:36,610
Use it to cure yourself.

39
00:03:36,610 --> 00:03:38,210
Sunwarm Jade?

40
00:03:38,210 --> 00:03:39,970
Impossible.

41
00:03:39,970 --> 00:03:41,490
Don't worry.

42
00:03:41,490 --> 00:03:44,020
This is the real Sunwarm Jade.

43
00:03:44,020 --> 00:03:46,100
I won't cause you harm.

44
00:04:41,400 --> 00:04:43,140
Li!

45
00:04:59,580 --> 00:05:02,000
His poison runs deep.

46
00:06:45,560 --> 00:06:47,170
Li.

47
00:06:51,360 --> 00:06:54,300
Li. You're awake.

48
00:06:55,260 --> 00:06:57,120
Li.

49
00:07:08,360 --> 00:07:10,070
Look.

50
00:07:12,560 --> 00:07:15,020
It's truly a Sunwarm Jade.

51
00:07:18,940 --> 00:07:21,410
Did I fall asleep just now?

52
00:07:21,410 --> 00:07:23,140
Yes, you did.

53
00:07:35,330 --> 00:07:38,410
I let out your blood just now to cure you.

54
00:07:38,410 --> 00:07:40,070
It was all back at the start.

55
00:07:40,070 --> 00:07:42,820
But now, it's red like normal blood.

56
00:07:42,820 --> 00:07:45,750
You would still be unconscious, otherwise.

57
00:07:48,330 --> 00:07:50,020
Let me do it.

58
00:08:15,460 --> 00:08:19,090
How did you get the jade?

59
00:08:19,090 --> 00:08:21,460
They couldn't possibly let you have it.

60
00:08:22,670 --> 00:08:27,210
Actually, my mother and sister are good people.

61
00:08:27,210 --> 00:08:29,820
They are often threatened by bad guys,

62
00:08:29,820 --> 00:08:32,500
so they hope you can stay to protect them.

63
00:08:32,500 --> 00:08:35,730
They do not harbor malice.

64
00:08:35,730 --> 00:08:37,860
They just can't see

65
00:08:39,880 --> 00:08:44,555
that Jiayuan City
isn't a place my father would stay in,

66
00:08:44,555 --> 00:08:46,945
let alone you.

67
00:08:54,190 --> 00:08:57,390
Drink this now. It's Chinese ginseng broth.

68
00:09:04,750 --> 00:09:09,137
My father gave me the jade as my dowry.

69
00:09:09,137 --> 00:09:12,430
My sisters have their own dowries too.

70
00:09:12,430 --> 00:09:16,720
But I told my mother that I'd never marry anyone.

71
00:09:16,720 --> 00:09:19,300
Therefore, I have no use for it.

72
00:09:27,190 --> 00:09:28,920
And this one here.

73
00:09:28,920 --> 00:09:30,560
Thrombus Pill.

74
00:09:53,970 --> 00:09:55,830
You like to heal people?

75
00:09:57,530 --> 00:10:00,610
I've learned some from the books
my father left behind.

76
00:10:01,360 --> 00:10:04,610
Your father was a great physician.

77
00:10:06,040 --> 00:10:08,330
Alas,

78
00:10:08,330 --> 00:10:10,530
he didn't want to be a physician.

79
00:10:10,530 --> 00:10:12,650
He wanted to be an immortal.

80
00:10:25,570 --> 00:10:28,290
Before this, I did not believe

81
00:10:28,290 --> 00:10:31,150
that the Sunwarm Jade was an excellent antidote.

82
00:10:31,150 --> 00:10:32,640
Me neither.

83
00:10:32,640 --> 00:10:34,980
Even though your father poisoned me,

84
00:10:35,750 --> 00:10:40,020
I trusted him when he told me that only the Sunwarm Jade could save me.

85
00:10:43,930 --> 00:10:45,290
No.

86
00:10:45,290 --> 00:10:48,030
He wasn't completely right.

87
00:10:49,000 --> 00:10:50,820
You saved me.

88
00:11:00,570 --> 00:11:02,510
Give me the jade.

89
00:11:05,200 --> 00:11:09,570
I mean I want to place it under the sun

90
00:11:09,570 --> 00:11:12,060
to see if its color can be restored.

91
00:11:14,630 --> 00:11:16,180
All right.

92
00:11:49,770 --> 00:11:52,660
Keep it. It's yours now.

93
00:12:02,910 --> 00:12:04,970
You should keep it.

94
00:12:14,240 --> 00:12:18,210
I Have a favor to ask.

95
00:12:20,440 --> 00:12:21,720
Speak.

96
00:12:21,720 --> 00:12:22,891
Who do you want killed?

97
00:12:22,891 --> 00:12:24,120
It's not that.

98
00:12:24,120 --> 00:12:26,340
I...

99
00:12:27,340 --> 00:12:32,160
I want you to take me with you.

100
00:12:42,600 --> 00:12:44,650
Sorry, I can't do that.

101
00:13:01,270 --> 00:13:03,060
Okay.

102
00:13:47,200 --> 00:13:51,030
Why don't you stay with the Mo Family for now?

103
00:13:51,030 --> 00:13:54,720
If someone bothers them, you can protect them.

104
00:13:55,327 --> 00:13:58,857
Once I find a place to cultivate and settle down,

105
00:13:58,857 --> 00:14:00,159
I'll come and pick you up.

106
00:14:00,159 --> 00:14:01,989
What do you think?

