 I have left. 

116
00:14:54,860 --> 00:14:56,790
 Qu Hun is a good friend of mine, 

117
00:14:56,790 --> 00:14:59,440
 and a great disciple of your father's. 

118
00:14:59,440 --> 00:15:01,550
 I entrust him to your hands. 

119
00:15:01,550 --> 00:15:05,650
 He should scare those
who wish to give you trouble. 

120
00:15:05,650 --> 00:15:08,720
 Please keep the vial. 

121
00:15:08,720 --> 00:15:10,690
 Take care. 

122
