 ♫ The wind whispers to the forest ♫ 

123
00:15:14,460 --> 00:15:19,820
 ♫ I wander into the dream under the clear galaxy ♫ 

124
00:15:23,260 --> 00:15:26,100
 ♫ This journey that spans across the universe ♫ 

125
00:15:26,100 --> 00:15:29,076
 ♫ Feels both familiar and unfamiliar ♫ 

126
00:15:29,076 --> 00:15:35,001
 ♫ Looking at the various faces of our world ♫ 

127
00:15:35,001 --> 00:15:37,960
 ♫ Each word, each utterance ♫ 

128
00:15:37,960 --> 00:15:40,270
 ♫ Carries the hopes of a lifetime... ♫ 

129
00:15:40,270 --> 00:15:41,580
Li!

130
00:15:41,580 --> 00:15:46,560
 ♫ Let's make the present count
and strive for a legacy ♫ 

131
00:15:46,560 --> 00:15:49,720
 ♫ Reunion and departure, searching around ♫ 

132
00:15:49,720 --> 00:15:52,520
 ♫ No one speaks the tongue I know ♫ 

133
00:15:52,520 --> 00:15:58,360
 ♫ Sadness follows me like a shadow ♫ 

134
00:15:58,360 --> 00:16:01,440
 ♫ I see the sky, the cloud,
the moon, and the star ♫ 

135
00:16:01,440 --> 00:16:04,300
 ♫ I see the wind and the rain ♫ 

136
00:16:04,300 --> 00:16:11,940
 ♫ There's no need to ask when I will return ♫ 

