138
00:17:16,390 --> 00:17:18,130
Ni Chang.

139
00:17:19,550 --> 00:17:21,960
Wan. It's been 20 years.

140
00:17:21,960 --> 00:17:24,760
 
You've finally left your cultivation.

141
00:17:29,000 --> 00:17:33,320
Ni Chang, what's new about the world?

142
00:17:33,320 --> 00:17:36,080
What else could it be?

143
00:17:36,080 --> 00:17:40,100
Just feuds and conflicts.

144
00:17:40,100 --> 00:17:42,670
Our grandmasters made the wise choice

145
00:17:42,670 --> 00:17:46,980
to forbid us from intervening
in the mortal's affairs.

146
00:17:47,720 --> 00:17:51,980
Indeed. Some like to whine
about how short life is.

147
00:17:51,980 --> 00:17:54,200
But if they are given
the opportunity to live longer,

148
00:17:54,200 --> 00:17:56,960
who knows what matter of oddity they will commit?

149
00:17:56,960 --> 00:18:00,790
You know this better than all of us.

150
00:18:00,790 --> 00:18:03,800
So why did you leave the mountain
to meddle in those affairs?

151
00:18:04,720 --> 00:18:07,790
Be it the demon sects or the dark cultivators,

152
00:18:07,790 --> 00:18:09,810
they are endless.

153
00:18:09,810 --> 00:18:14,360
You should focus on your cultivation
and ignore them.

154
00:18:15,140 --> 00:18:17,960
You sure are indifferent, Ni Chang.

155
00:18:17,960 --> 00:18:20,360
But I study the Maiden Cycle Technique.

156
00:18:20,360 --> 00:18:22,480
It requires me to be at peace.

157
00:18:22,480 --> 00:18:27,500
I hate strife so I must leave to intervene.

158
00:18:27,500 --> 00:18:29,080
You never listen to me.

159
00:18:29,080 --> 00:18:30,860
The mortal affairs are the most potent venom.

160
00:18:30,860 --> 00:18:33,360
Make sure you don't get too involved.

161
00:18:33,360 --> 00:18:36,020
Don't worry, Ni Chang.

162
00:18:36,020 --> 00:18:39,080
I'm planning to visit the six other sects first.

163
00:18:39,080 --> 00:18:42,750
Then, I'll check if they are dark cultivators
and demon sects roaming about.

164
00:18:42,750 --> 00:18:44,450
I'll be back soon.

165
00:18:44,450 --> 00:18:51,190
Do not forget that we are to host the next Immortal Ascension Trials.

166
00:18:51,190 --> 00:18:53,420
Worry not, Ni Chang.

167
00:18:57,790 --> 00:18:59,210
 Cultivators 

168
00:18:59,210 --> 00:19:02,270
 
 rarely appear in crowded places. 

169
00:19:02,270 --> 00:19:04,430
 Where do they usually go? 

170
00:19:05,010 --> 00:19:07,960
 Are there truly cultivators in Tainan Valley? 

171
00:19:08,830 --> 00:19:12,970
 I want to see what they see. 

172
00:19:13,900 --> 00:19:17,040
 The valley a hundred li south of Jiayuan City 

173
00:19:17,040 --> 00:19:19,700
 is shrouded by mists all year round. 

174
00:19:20,796 --> 00:19:25,216
 According to the scroll,
Tainan Valley should be here. 

175
00:19:39,280 --> 00:19:42,420
 

176
00:19:48,170 --> 00:19:49,310
I am Wan Xiao Shan.

177
00:19:49,310 --> 00:19:51,320
How may I address you?

178
00:19:53,007 --> 00:19:54,600
Han Li.

179
00:19:54,600 --> 00:19:56,290
Your name is Han Li, I see.

180
00:19:56,290 --> 00:19:58,110
You're alone here.

181
00:19:58,110 --> 00:20:00,410
You must be a rogue cultivator
who wishes to enter Tainan Valley.

182
00:20:00,410 --> 00:20:03,060
You know what? Let's band up.

183
00:20:03,060 --> 00:20:04,900
Band up?

184
00:20:06,170 --> 00:20:07,950
Are you perhaps lost?

185
00:20:07,950 --> 00:20:10,690
Han, don't underestimate me.

186
00:20:10,690 --> 00:20:12,650
Even though I'm an elementary cultivator,

187
00:20:12,650 --> 00:20:17,180
I know very well how to get to Tainan Valley.

188
00:20:19,070 --> 00:20:20,140
All right, then.

189
00:20:20,140 --> 00:20:21,270
Let's travel together.

190
00:20:21,270 --> 00:20:22,310
Lead the way.

191
00:20:22,310 --> 00:20:23,970
Follow me.

192
00:20:28,160 --> 00:20:30,350
What do you mean by a rogue cultivator?

193
00:20:30,350 --> 00:20:32,000
Like us,

194
00:20:32,000 --> 00:20:34,590
we do not belong
to those seven sects like Moonshadow Sect

195
00:20:34,590 --> 00:20:36,680
or hail from a cultivator clan like the Yans.

196
00:20:36,680 --> 00:20:39,730
We cultivate alone
so we are the rogue cultivators.

197
00:20:42,880 --> 00:20:46,300
 He seems to know quite a lot about cultivation. 

198
00:20:46,300 --> 00:20:48,860
 Perhaps I can get more out of him. 

199
00:20:52,030 --> 00:20:57,750
Wan, do you know of a way
to dispel the mist before us?

200
00:20:57,750 --> 00:21:00,940
Han, you must have only
become a cultivator recently.

201
00:21:00,940 --> 00:21:04,031
This misty barrier only opens up
once every ten years.

202
00:21:04,031 --> 00:21:05,272
If we can't enter the valley,

203
00:21:05,272 --> 00:21:08,030
it means it is not the right moment yet.

204
00:21:08,030 --> 00:21:10,860
Come. Have some fruit.

205
00:21:13,780 --> 00:21:17,900
They say immortals do not eat rice.

206
00:21:17,900 --> 00:21:20,490
They ingest wind and pebbles
and drink morning dew.

207
00:21:20,490 --> 00:21:23,040
That's not true then.

208
00:21:25,440 --> 00:21:28,060
Only immortals do that.

209
00:21:28,060 --> 00:21:30,720
People like us are called cultivators.

210
00:21:30,720 --> 00:21:34,520
Immortals live as long as the universe.

211
00:21:35,170 --> 00:21:37,300
They live as long as the universe?

212
00:21:37,300 --> 00:21:39,780
No wonder Physician Mo did everything
to become one.

213
00:21:39,780 --> 00:21:41,580
But considering our current cultivation progress,

214
00:21:41,580 --> 00:21:44,240
we can only live a century at most.

215
00:21:44,930 --> 00:21:47,100
That's not bad already.

216
00:21:48,030 --> 00:21:50,010
It's open!

217
00:21:54,310 --> 00:21:56,090
Wan.

218
00:21:57,140 --> 00:21:58,240
Wan?

219
00:21:58,240 --> 00:22:00,310
Come in.

220
00:22:02,450 --> 00:22:04,310
Check out this Glacial Sword.

221
00:22:04,310 --> 00:22:05,960
- Check out this Glacial Sword.
- Advanced Ice Talisman.

222
00:22:05,960 --> 00:22:07,480
Three gems for one talisman.

223
00:22:07,480 --> 00:22:09,010
Check this out.

224
00:22:09,010 --> 00:22:12,620
- Wan, this is...
- This is Tainan Bazaar.

225
00:22:12,620 --> 00:22:14,780
It Lasts for three days.

226
00:22:14,780 --> 00:22:16,790
We're lucky to run into its opening.

227
00:22:16,790 --> 00:22:19,560
This is a fair price already.

228
00:22:21,030 --> 00:22:24,100
- 20 gems.
- Come. Take a look.

229
00:22:24,680 --> 00:22:27,490
Come. A century-old ironcoil snake.

230
00:22:27,490 --> 00:22:29,350
It took me a lot to catch it.

231
00:22:29,350 --> 00:22:30,580
Glacial Sword!

232
00:22:30,580 --> 00:22:32,510
Check out my Glacial Sword.

233
00:22:32,510 --> 00:22:34,110
20 gems for one.

234
00:22:34,110 --> 00:22:35,270
Talisman.

235
00:22:35,270 --> 00:22:36,550
Do you want any? Take a look.

236
00:22:36,550 --> 00:22:38,280
- Come.
- Come take a look.

237
00:22:39,030 --> 00:22:41,550
My friend, come browse my wares.

238
00:22:41,550 --> 00:22:43,170
- Come.
- Advanced Ice...

239
00:22:43,170 --> 00:22:45,740
Advanced Ice Talisman for three gems only.

240
00:22:46,340 --> 00:22:48,310
Common items like these aren't very useful.

241
00:22:48,310 --> 00:22:50,190
They are common?

242
00:22:54,060 --> 00:22:56,550
You need gems to buy them. Do you have any?

243
00:22:56,550 --> 00:23:00,010
Besides, it's a rip-off.

244
00:23:00,010 --> 00:23:05,080
Are gems the currency among cultivators?

245
00:23:05,820 --> 00:23:07,760
Come on, Han.

246
00:23:10,900 --> 00:23:15,480
As the name suggests, a gem is a stone filled with spiritual aura.

247
00:23:17,140 --> 00:23:19,170
A good gem is transparent and bright.

248
00:23:19,170 --> 00:23:21,800
You can use it as a source of light.

249
00:23:23,480 --> 00:23:25,820
This is already a very fair price.

250
00:23:25,820 --> 00:23:30,066
Mine is not as good, but it's good enough to provide energy

251
00:23:30,066 --> 00:23:33,810
for an array or to restore your spiritual power
after a battle.

252
00:23:59,100 --> 00:24:00,970
Another rogue cultivator.

253
00:24:00,970 --> 00:24:02,410
How many has it been?

254
00:24:02,410 --> 00:24:05,290
Grandmaster, this is the seventh.

255
00:24:06,300 --> 00:24:09,620
Grandmaster, I found this nearby.

256
00:24:09,620 --> 00:24:10,820
 
Yan?

257
00:24:10,820 --> 00:24:12,540
From the Yan Clan Stronghold?
 

258
00:24:12,540 --> 00:24:16,030
Those clan disciples
love to bully rogue cultivators.

259
00:24:16,030 --> 00:24:17,340
Enough.

260
00:24:17,340 --> 00:24:19,300
Do not jump to conclusions
before we investigate thoroughly.

261
00:24:19,300 --> 00:24:20,860
Yes.

262
00:24:20,860 --> 00:24:22,440
The barrier has been lifted.

263
00:24:22,440 --> 00:24:26,060
The valley is now filled
with rogue and clan disciples.

264
00:24:26,060 --> 00:24:29,470
Both parties are not on good terms, so anything could happen.

265
00:24:30,356 --> 00:24:35,100
Yu, Qing, Dispatch more disciples to guard the valley.

266
00:24:35,100 --> 00:24:39,182
